Slow-mo throwback to the time Salt Bae sprinkled his arm salt all over my ribeye 😛🧂🥩 The crouch he does at the end also kills me 😂😂😂

Who remembers when this guy was a “thing”? How many of you have tried his restaurants? Did you love it, like it, or hate it?

My thoughts: incredibly overpriced and the server continually tried to push us to order the most expensive items 🙄 Most of the food was ok (nothing special), and while the ribeye was very expensive for what it was, I did enjoy the taste. Would I go back? Nope - it’s definitely a one and done place. And if I would have went and Mr. Bae wasn’t there to do all the gimmicks, it would have been a MAJOR BUST 🫠
